          <h3>Main projects</h3>
          <a href="#">Electronic Document Management System (EDMS)</a>
          <p>Converting patient casenotes into an electronic format so that they can be viewed and managed on screen 24/7</p>
          <a href="#">Electronic Patient Record (EPR)</a>
          <p>Recording of all patient information electronically on one system. Will
            enable information sharing, electronic prescribing and electronic clinic
            management</p>
          <a href="#">Clinical Portal (CP)</a>
          <p>Linking up of all existing computer systems, meaning you only have to log
            in once to view all patient information systems on one screen. Enables
            secure sharing of patient information across the NHS.</p>
